measure.name: utility_bill_calculations_detailed
measure.description: Calls the SAM SDK for calculating utility bills.
measure.modeler_description: Calls the utilityrate3 module in the SAM SDK.

argument.name: custom_tariff
argument.description: Absolute (or relative) path to custom tariff file.

argument.name: ng_fixed
argument.description: Monthly fixed charge for natural gas.

argument.name: ng_rate
argument.description: Price per therm for natural gas.

argument.name: oil_rate
argument.description: Price per gallon for fuel oil.

argument.name: pv_compensation_type
argument.description: The type of compensation for PV.

argument.name: pv_sellback_rate
argument.display_name: PV: Net Metering Annual Excess Sellback Rate
argument.description: The annual excess/net sellback rate for PV. Only applies if the PV compensation type is 'Net Metering'.

argument.name: pv_tariff_rate
argument.description: The annual full/gross tariff rate for PV. Only applies if the PV compensation type is 'Feed-In Tariff'.
